title: Modern & Bright Studio! NE Minneapolis!
posting_body: ['Lease at Frances TODAY!', 'Managed by Solhem, Frances is located in the heart of the Northeast Arts District and just minutes from Downtown.', 'Walk your dog along the river, bike throughout the quiet NE streets, and immerse yourself in everything this neighborhood has to offer!', 'Frances is a sister property to Lucille and The Julia, located a half-block from Broadway.', 'Frances features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck and efficient, upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', '#421 -- Plan L', 'Please note, our online pricing shows the effective monthly rate when factoring in our current specials.', 'However, you would use the special up-front and pay regular market rent of $1,315/mo afterwards.', '#421 is finished with vinyl oak plank flooring and gray marbled quartz countertops.', ' This unit also features full size washer/dryer and a smart, functional walk-through design.', 'Note: Photos are of an lower floor unit.', 'For more info and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @solhemcompanies', 'Frances is managed by locally-owned Solhem Companies: <URL>', 'Prices and specials subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction -- Locally Owned -- Solhem']
